<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>赠送卡券</title>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=Edge">
    <meta content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1,maximum-scale=1,user-scalable=no" name="viewport">
    <meta name="format-detection" content="telephone=no" />

    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./css/common.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./css/reset.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./css/donateCard.css">
  </head>
  <body>
    <section class="tab1 down-border">
      <p>赠送卡券</p>
    </section>
    <p class="word1">您的免费洗车权益剩余20次，请选择您要赠送的数量：</p>
    <section class="tab-panel tab2">
      <div class="box">
        <p>总次数</p>
        <div class="amount">
          <p>0</p>
          <p>次</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <p class="word2">所填张数不能为0，且不能超过您当前剩余的总次数；</p>
    <section class="tab-panel tab3">
      <div class="box">
        <p>留言</p>
        <p>我在D+护车给你们送福利了，先到先得~</p>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section class="tab-panel tab4">
      <div class="box">
        <p>每人有且只能领取一次</p>
        <input type="checkbox" class="check" value="">
      </div>
    </section>
    <section class="tab5">
      <p>价值</p>
      <p class="num">0.00</p>
      <p>元</p>
    </section>
    <div class="tab-panel btn">确定赠送</div>
    <script type="text/javascript">
    var btn = document.getElementsByClassName('btn')[0];
    btn.addEventListener("click",function(){
      window.location.href = "./myvip.html";
    })


    </script>
  </body>
</html>
